 experience.  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/607080/extras/28798650bed03e7c0f5f6087c171531a.poster.avif?t=1745521663\" width=608 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/607080/extras/28798650bed03e7c0f5f6087c171531a.webm?t=1745521663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/607080/extras/28798650bed03e7c0f5f6087c171531a.mp4?t=1745521663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wield a powerful array of psychic powers to blast, burn and levitate things, or even slow down time itself to solve environmental puzzles and battle strange enemies.</p></li></ul>",
